CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A13, reads: "D.I.'s 'Atlantic City, USA' Thrills Patrons at Press Club Summer Revue"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gloria Golden Grate wearing floral dress with puffed sleeves and light colored gloves, holding floral coat with light colored lining, posing in her home in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue held in the Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn
